snippet: On Sunday, Molchanova, regarded as the greatest free diver in history, attempted a recreational dive to a depth that was modest for her. She never resurfaced.
abstract: Russian woman Natalia Molchanova, seen as greatest free diver in history, disappears during recreational dive off island near Ibiza, Spain; Molchanova, who holds dozens of world diving records,  is not expected to be found alive after two days of search efforts.
lead_paragraph: On Sunday, Molchanova, regarded as the greatest free diver in history, attempted a recreational dive to a depth that was modest for her. She never resurfaced.

headline.main: Free Diver Natalia Molchanova Descends for Fun, Then Vanishes
headline.print_headline: A Star Diver Descends for Fun, and Vanishes
